V070B41N   EFAR41N   x070B410  (Cx) (CL+)

V070B41P   EFAR41P   x070B411  (Cx) (711) (T-)
V070B41Q   EFAR41Q   x070B411  (Cx) (711) (T+)
V070B41R   EFAR41R   x070B411  (Cx) (711) (CL-)
V070B41S   EFAR41S   x070B411  (Cx) (711) (CL+)

V070B41T   EFAR41T   x070B412  (Cx) (310) (T-)
V070B41U   EFAR41U   x070B412  (Cx) (310) (T+)
V070B41V   EFAR41V   x070B412  (Cx) (310) (CL-)
V070B41W   EFAR41W   x070B412  (Cx) (310) (CL+)

V070B41X   EFAR41X   '41G      (Cx) with 486-cache default max waitstate


Note - (Cx) - Vers 41G-41W  require specific "design-in" considerations for
       Cyrix 486DLC.  These pins must be connected:  #KEN, #A20M.

       These versions give best Cyrix performance (compared with "retrofit"
       versions), but will MALFUNCTION unless the board is designed for it.


